whether the package includes \"WrappedReferenceMap\" and if it implements the Serializable interface. This sounds important, as ensuring compatibility with serialization might affect how objects are handled within the package. I’ll need to dig into the documentation or source code to confirm those details. Once I figure that out, it should help gauge its usability in various contexts. Let's see what I can find!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03f7d34eced8103b016a41e74bf38881979681020e3ee41c71\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQedWMs1s2xdv_IvLsTVMTPol3l35CVmPDY0A6jm4mXau2HuvtLdwS2Yr2L3hs7YrMAEr0VP-d1W0A-dKW1Ylmo_nforqyckNjWW9p3b4b2nTKOfd2aD4W_4dwhbmnQW8bhjDkKUh0M1LJrk2zUcqX-Tybi5dlP41boeGndOgmnRMQMz_2juYxYSu_Cxgdj-S6pa_v6xn-O8H6H2tVCZ9S8W8eGPA7fXMVhyQ5byjFEsP_P-LpKVvUe8WAhs60xMuHX4ZkL5Ib1SMNrwzpFHXkhjqZyIcv0SRCbbLDF_wna0oDaBiTbi5awHB7owrDSdUMjyi3LSMPySb4D0uH4lcrRtwzzkyDjpZBKTVLBTQp72xkSdjXseuIbFfOkjXjd7lUvK0BVpCwDtwWZhQE5er27SYEeICiTSmpuQsyL-uWNaOcJS-tzMJUN3CHlFjWeM4PGxfCr8arBjdYceX-g4XsjwT1-E4HqGkTD0hZ0yx3AiN51TXSu60sWrrGC2dWmr-uOwgiJ_4NnIcjsjfoQ9k9iVAgI4eV47eUI68ybhNIK00_UA-JKDaEvJVJ41XPoUiRA8leemeIQxuD04XbCYpcp8SI9pFrn9mbmVcfp_kkpGTYYonZcfy4JTVlo71YJ6KWZvfwhWVHnib8_dndCmwjNzsqf34aL1LnldMhZ8XU-xi6kePLHS1BzrEb04WVKfJeaDSotNPLe0gCQNdugnMA5DeDo4Opwcf8OOzZY7ivPAgx9tBMSNSFHrA096Rfzh0vkKfqb_W_02fkN7DkSQbihMmry2kQpTtmEU_z21rcVC6iI8y-dUD6THzfnyIoL3toM8ngQMQ1zxw6d2DeAGT73aQt56g6SAFp-abGyzuQCuChUmo5-Rvi_Ht3LySrxJT7VY1BJC4tS2UxEqyp2T-hm5JANpRVtQtreOZuEBDvTfFzgYOJRNdQNB2S1g98szFl6-mwipbSk_6J6pNwYZ1WquvoJ9nkb1VQRM-pMkIbCxhzjmysN068wiMGJl2lIR_s5FlhnRHl8_o-3mHmnMGNiGQ80dLbF28OR1EEuWAJmD5jt-0grV5CSRF972qqzhcsePZBOVI4Zll6kysoKIy1wl3uR6zM3PWiEJ2ZNEx8XHTtymDkwDUeafjUFHLwTgk0LCDBe91wzr4gbqGAFiNEPLP3hhqbnFVIjIokjb-8ulMyJnCD_nYcTCkvtTUJ7d9IkDaVXbW2jYjJv1IIB6cXSKt_TOQhd6Hl98JW2jKyWAAkVp2r125jfQ4uY8QOuH3ZRljXMeuhUdSgWvA78tWgWb30C5yFl7KfAGrkOrfgu56q1KuxYvhfKaF40mfzUQBR1aRmh8EpXjYD-9qMzuM-No4v2Jmd3w7KxDvthD5EBV2E4JTB3bSyJslp7d53E9CY9Hd9tXCiyyyOtXtA