hia/morphia/ReferenceMapTest.java`\n\nIt verifies public `ReferenceMap` behavior and documents that standard Java serialization cannot reach the private hooks. The six remaining dynamic-access call sites should be left uncovered for this artifact version.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03f7d34eced8103b016a41e92908288197b774e9849d6f47c4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6632, "output": 1762, "cacheRead": 35328, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 43722, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782704397492, "responseId": "resp_03f7d34eced8103b016a41e90f1078819786927a6ccf77bd5b"}, "toolResults": []}
